GCODING.item: ** Get only condensing material - product hierarchy level 2 = CDU)
* READ TABLE lt_mara INTO ls_mara WITH KEY matnr = ls_gen-material.
* FIND FIRST OCCURRENCE OF ' CDU ' IN ls_mara-prdha.
* READ TABLE lt_prodh INTO ls_prodh WITH KEY prod_hier = lv_prdha.
* READ TABLE lt_adrc INTO ls_adrc WITH KEY addrnumber = ls_adr-addr_no.

CODE.item: DATA: lt_prodh TYPE TABLE OF bapimat_prodh.
READ TABLE lt_prodh INTO ls_prodh WITH KEY prod_hier = lv_prdha.
